OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be mostly cloudy with
OL,6,Frain or showers, but drier and
OL,7,Fbrighter across Shetland during the
OL,8,Fmorning. Winds light or moderate from
OL,9,Fthe east or southeast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers clearing Shetland
OL,12,Fthis evening leaving some late sunny
OL,13,Fthen clear spells overnight. Cloudier
OL,14,Ffor Orkney with patchy rain at first
OL,15,Fbut becoming dry with clearer spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,19,Fgood sunny spells. However the odd
OL,20,Flight afternoon shower not to be ruled
OL,21,Fout for Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
