OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FWindy
OL,6,Fand rather cloudy on Tuesday with a
OL,7,Ffew outbreaks of rain. Further showers
OL,8,Fon Wednesday but winds easing. Drier
OL,9,Fand sunnier spells developing on
OL,10,FThursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
